      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="05500447-f0b7-45a4-b759-f9826bd65a46" type="Noun">
          <Vi>hoàng tử</Vi>
          <En>A male member of a royal family, especially the son of a king or queen.</En>
          <Example>The prince announced his engagement to a commoner.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="644d8fc9-32ca-4636-8bbc-4ba9e0b01a3f">
              <Vi>Chỉ con trai của vua hoặc hoàng hậu trong các nước quân chủ.</Vi>
              <En>Refers to the son of a king or queen in monarchies.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="a169dc8e-c8eb-40b2-b7df-54e043f2a6b3">
              <Vi>Đôi khi dùng để chỉ người đàn ông cao quý, đẹp trai hoặc được yêu quý (nghĩa bóng).</Vi>
              <En>Used metaphorically to describe a charming, noble, or beloved man (e.g., "prince charming").</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
        </Meaning>
      </Meanings>
